article.headline: Wilkerson scores 27, Sam Houston takes down Middle Tennessee 60-51
article.description: — Lamar Wilkerson scored 27 points as Sam Houston beat Middle Tennessee 60-51 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Wilkerson scores 27, Sam Houston takes down Middle Tennessee 60-51
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — Lamar Wilkerson scored 27 points as Sam Houston beat Middle Tennessee 60-51 on Saturday night. Wilkerson was 8 of 15 shooting, including 2 for 5 from 3-point range, and went 9 for 10 from the line for the Bearkats (10-8, 3-0 Conference USA). Souleymane Doumbia scored 10 points and added eight rebounds. The Blue Raiders (6-11, 0-2) were led by Jestin Porter, who posted 29 points. Elias King added 10 points, six rebounds and two blocks for Middle Tennessee. I ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
